He sees Tiger tanks, two of them.

1543
02:07:12,459 --> 02:07:14,461
Panzer tanks, two of them.

1544
02:07:14,587 --> 02:07:16,380
Infantry.

1545
02:07:16,463 --> 02:07:18,340
Fifty plus change.

1546
02:07:27,266 --> 02:07:29,059
Disperse! You know what to do!

1547
02:07:29,143 --> 02:07:30,839
- Reiben, get on the rabbit.
- Yes, sir.

1548
02:07:30,939 --> 02:07:34,148
«- Upham, get some cover.
- Mellish and Henderson, lock and load!»

1549
02:07:34,273 --> 02:07:37,193
«- This is it.
- Everybody check your ammo!»

1550
02:07:37,860 --> 02:07:39,153
«Good luck, Reiben.»

1551
02:07:39,278 --> 02:07:42,615
