1554
02:07:58,797 --> 02:08:02,885
Yeah? Why don't you check
the head space and she should run.

1555
02:08:10,726 --> 02:08:12,937
Upham! Hustle up!

1556
02:09:03,279 --> 02:09:04,947
- Corporal Upham?
- Yes, sir.

1557
02:09:05,030 --> 02:09:07,422
