02:16:39,276 --> 02:16:40,861
- Ryan!
«- Get off me!»

1585
02:16:40,986 --> 02:16:43,447
- Are you all right?
- Get off me!

1586
02:16:43,530 --> 02:16:45,657
Yeah, yeah,
I'm fine, too, Captain. Thanks.

1587
02:16:46,533 --> 02:16:51,163
Okay, both sides!
Get aboard! Get a grenade in there!

1588
02:16:54,166 --> 02:16:55,667
Grenade!

1589
02:16:57,502 --> 02:16:59,171
20-mill!

1590
02:17:00,630 --> 02:17:03,341
Flak gun, 20 millimeter. Take it out!

1591
02:17:15,687 --> 02:17:19,191
Heavy weapon in defilade below!
I ain't got a shot!

1592
02:17:23,695 --> 02:17:25,447
Pincer move, Parker!

1593
02:17:25,530 --> 02:17:28,033
- Targets 8 o'clock low!
«- Shit!»

1594
02:17:28,116 --> 02:17:30,368
God grant me strength.

1595
02:17:44,257 --> 02:17:45,801
Displace!

1596
02:17:45,884 --> 02:17:47,302
Come on!

1597
02:18:03,109 --> 02:18:05,862
Cover, Upham! Cover! Cover!

1598
02:18:22,629 --> 02:18:24,589
I'm out of 30-caliber.

1599
02:18:28,009 --> 02:18:30,846
Blessed be the Lord, my strength,
which teaches my hands to war

1600
02:18:30,929 --> 02:18:33,306
and my fingers to fight.

1601
02:18:41,815 --> 02:18:44,317
My goodness and my fortress,

1602
02:18:44,401 --> 02:18:47,070
my high tower and my deliverer,

1603
02:18:49,656 --> 02:18:52,868
my shield and he in whom I trust.

1604
02:18:55,912 --> 02:18:57,998
Come here, baby.

1605
02:19:20,604 --> 02:19:22,397
Parker, get down!

1606
02:19:44,085 --> 02:19:46,504
Captain, that 20-millimeter's
killing us.

1607
02:19:46,588 --> 02:19:48,882
We gotta try to flank it somehow.

1608
02:19:49,007 --> 02:19:51,843
Well, let me get over for the top shot.

1609
