1618
02:24:31,122 --> 02:24:34,079
Let's stop. Let's stop. Let's stop.
Listen to me! Listen to me! Stop!

1619
02:24:34,179 --> 02:24:35,931
Stop! Don't...

1620
02:25:12,580 --> 02:25:17,418
Son of a bitch!
Son of a bitch! Son of a bitch!

1621
02:25:17,502 --> 02:25:19,295
Son of a bitch!

1622
02:25:20,755 --> 02:25:21,798
Bitch!

1623
02:26:40,835 --> 02:26:43,921
- I'm out.
- Those 60 rounds.

1624
02:26:45,340 --> 02:26:48,509
- We can use them without the tube.
- How?

1625
02:26:48,593 --> 02:26:51,554
Fuse-arming wire, set back, heave it!

1626
02:27:07,278 --> 02:27:08,946
Panzerschreck!

1627
02:27:42,980 --> 02:27:45,233
We're going to the Alamo.

1628
02:27:55,451 --> 02:27:57,286
Alamo! Alamo!

1629
02:28:16,848 --> 02:28:19,142
We'll take it! You fall back!

1630
02:28:19,267 --> 02:28:22,854
- You be right behind us!
- Soon as we're in business!

1631
02:28:26,816 --> 02:28:28,943
Displace. Reiben.

1632
02:28:31,446 --> 02:28:32,864
Reload.

1633
02:29:21,704 --> 02:29:23,206
All right, go.

1634
02:29:24,479 --> 02:29:25,566
We're blowing the bridge!

1635
02:29:25,666 --> 02:29:28,544
